OL,3,CTemperatures to drop this week as
OL,4,Ccolder air spreads south
OL,6,FThe UK's recent mild spell is about to
OL,7,Fgive way to a much colder feel.
OL,9,FAs winds turn northerly this week,
OL,10,Fcolder air will spread south across
OL,11,Fthe country, sending temperatures
OL,12,Ftumbling and bringing the chance of
OL,13,Fsnow showers for some.
OL,15,FOver the next few days, many places
OL,16,Fwill feel dramatically colder than
OL,17,Fthey did just a few days earlier.
OL,19,FWhy is the weather changing?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
