OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773165969
OL,3,CTemperatures to drop this week as
OL,4,Ccolder air spreads south
OL,6,FThe shift in conditions is being
OL,7,Fdriven by a change in wind direction
OL,8,Fbehind a passing weather system.
OL,10,FAs this system clears away to the
OL,11,Feast, colder air from the Arctic will
OL,12,Fbegin moving southwards across the UK.
OL,13,FNortherly winds will draw this colder
OL,14,Fair down across Scotland first before
OL,15,Fit gradually spreads further south
OL,16,Finto England and Wales.
OL,18,FThis pattern often brings a noticeable
OL,19,Fdrop in both daytime and overnight
OL,20,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
