PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773165969
OL,3,CTemperatures to drop this week as
OL,4,Ccolder air spreads south
OL,6,FWhen will temperatures start to fall?
OL,8,FThe change will begin to develop on
OL,9,FThursday, with colder air starting to
OL,10,Fmove into northern parts of the UK.
OL,12,FBy Friday, the chill will be felt more
OL,13,Fwidely as the colder air mass
OL,14,Fcontinues pushing south. Daytime
OL,15,Ftemperatures in many areas will be
OL,16,Fseveral degrees lower than earlier in
OL,17,Fthe week.
OL,19,FCombined with the breeze, it may feel
OL,20,Fparticularly cold compared with the
OL,21,Frecent mild conditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
