PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773165969
OL,3,CTemperatures to drop this week as
OL,4,Ccolder air spreads south
OL,6,FHow cold will it get?
OL,8,FEarlier in the week, temperatures
OL,9,Freached around 12 to 14C in parts of
OL,10,Fsouthern England.
OL,12,FBy the end of the working week, many
OL,13,Fareas may struggle to reach daytime
OL,14,Fhighs of 5 to 7C, particularly across
OL,15,Fnorthern and eastern regions. With a
OL,16,Fbrisk breeze expected on Friday, wind
OL,17,Fchill could make it feel close to
OL,18,Ffreezing.
OL,26,@qD@XOXvD@POX
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
