OL,3,CTemperatures to drop this week as
OL,4,Ccolder air spreads south
OL,6,FGardeners should also be aware that
OL,7,Fwhere skies clear overnight,
OL,8,Ftemperatures may fall low enough for
OL,9,Ffrost to develop in some locations.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FWhere could snow fall?
OL,18,FThe colder air may allow some showers
OL,19,Fto turn wintry, particularly across
OL,20,Fnorthern parts of the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
