OL,3,CTemperatures to drop this week as
OL,4,Ccolder air spreads south
OL,6,FHow long will it last?
OL,8,FThe colder conditions are expected to
OL,9,Fpersist for several days.
OL,11,FHowever, longer-range forecasts
OL,12,Fsuggest temperatures may begin to
OL,13,Frecover into next week as Atlantic
OL,14,Fweather systems move back towards the
OL,15,FUK, potentially bringing milder air
OL,16,Fonce again.
OL,18,FThe coming days may bring a brief
OL,19,Freminder of winter before milder
OL,20,Fspring conditions begin returning next
OL,21,Fweek.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
